n explanation\">No_keywords</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">2. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"80\" name=\"question-2\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Confusion about what it means to be green.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-2 explain-area-80\" data-qnumber=\"80\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 2 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">F</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-80\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-80\" data-qnumber=\"80\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"5\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\">No_keywords</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">3. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"81\" name=\"question-3\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option></select> <span style=\"font-size: